{"tid":1692170,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"建議所有毒撚申請白卡同任何政府福利","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:06:29.000Z","uid":312242,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db29cf2270b008ede9bf8710e9e22475aa87d760","tid":1692170,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"毒撚, 社會都冇當過我哋係人 日日係咁逼害我哋<br />\n<br />\n笑鳩我哋係毒撚 隊撚咁我哋落地底層嗰度 我哋要日日受佢哋嘅壓迫<br />\n<br />\n你可能話我癡線我精神分裂 但你是問下你自己係咪你嘅social circle嘅最低層? 你係咪冇女? 員工同事同學係咪成日撚你?<br />\n<br />\n咁即係即係話我哋係畀人oppressed緊囉 畀番啲著數我哋係值得嘅<br />\n<br />\n我propose 你哋全部申請白卡綜援公屋任何所有嘅政府福利 <br />\n呢個時勢嗰個政府你唔攞佢錢嘅佢都畀啲支那人或者嗰啲白色大象工程例如大灣區建設沙中線等等嘅嘢 最好又食撚曬佢啲資源<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣每個月啦佢錢 其實仲有效過抵制乜嘢藍絲商店TVB等等<br />\n<br />\n咁有咩優惠呢? 白卡佬就可以搭車兩蚊, 包括黨鐵巴士仲有去長洲嘅快船 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有你哋可以去海洋公園特快排隊仲有唔知咩遊樂場優惠但 who cares?<br />\n<br />\n白卡津貼仲會每個月畀好似一千蚊你 as long 你架每幾個月去睇一次精神科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔係好冇面嘅 仲有你要講到自己幾痴線幾辛苦佢就會持續批你呀<br />\n<br />\n利申:白卡佬 (咩事我唔講)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeS7B6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeS7B6b.jpg&h=85cad472&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8b1688bebfdb08189f41ffef0db37dbbadc264a","tid":1692170,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ff953a2c541da6388c500d23424aa892f0dad68","tid":1692170,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8b1688bebfdb08189f41ffef0db37dbbadc264a","tid":1692170,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:15:04.000Z","msg":"都話咗咩事我唔講喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f32021c8743454d468649361bcd68de76c8b2df","tid":1692170,"uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"我要一人一信投訴TVB<br />\n過五十萬 之後轉去國際戰線 <br />\n向外國輸出 電視台失信 <br />\n<br />\n等東南亞cut左TVB佢[/quote]"},{"pid":"968bc4cea4450d81d1c8cc05ca3d3dba161990f1","tid":1692170,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b3468315c0e0fb1ee309c0119bbc9c9ad9397f0","tid":1692170,"uid":110509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"全民白卡綜緩"},{"pid":"21df2d745cbdee973180d94bce57d399d8ab361c","tid":1692170,"uid":157948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:26:25.000Z","msg":"全民白咭老綜算9數<br />\n<br />\n香港新四大天王：《白卡，殘津，綜援，公屋》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/628040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/628040</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n利申:拎左殘津成年"},{"pid":"2c7e1159d753cdcb68e489c239add6d8b286fac7","tid":1692170,"uid":312242,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"968bc4cea4450d81d1c8cc05ca3d3dba161990f1","tid":1692170,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ff953a2c541da6388c500d23424aa892f0dad68","tid":1692170,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8b1688bebfdb08189f41ffef0db37dbbadc264a","tid":1692170,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:15:04.000Z","msg":"都話咗咩事我唔講喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:28:56.000Z","msg":"智商根據MENSA 115 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我可以話畀你聽其實我個症狀同情緒有關 根本是好輕微 (compared to 啲斬人嘅廢老痴線佬) 唔值得所謂嘅傷殘label <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有免費午餐你唔攞先傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n向政府攞資源加速攬炒又可以食免費午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" c